flare multicore (HttpServer.serve(..., num_workers=N), v0.4.0). N pthread
workers each bound to the same port with SO_REUSEPORT. Worker count comes
from FLARE_BENCH_WORKERS (default 4) and pinning from FLARE_BENCH_PIN
(default 1, pin_to_cpu). Version recorded in env.json as the current
git commit sha at bench time.
